description:
The Law of God - the 10 Commandments. Law and Grace. These issues have been the subject of great confusion in the religious world. Well-meaning Christians have lost sight of the meaning and purpose of Gods law. Many modern pastors and church members have accepted the teaching that the 10 Commandments are no longer binding since we are under grace, and not under the law. What does the Bible say about this? You will also learn the difference between the law of God and law of Moses. You will see how Jesus' death on the cross relates to God's Law and it's relevance today. You will discover God's standard that He will use to judge all human beings. You owe it to yourself to properly understand this life or death topic - your very salvation is at stake!
